reviewText: I love Shelba Stanga because he plays himself and that why he is so real. Need to make more DVD of Shelby and what he is doing now and how he lives since he is a millionaire
I LOVE WATCHING SHELBY AND ALL THE CRAZY THINGS HE DOES. THIS SEASON SERIES IS A MUST HAVE AND MOST DEFINITELY RECOMMEND. ITEM ARRIVED ON TIME.

If you like stories of Louisiana swamps, Shelby it is.  He is a kind man, and thinks of others, although he is on the "wild side" in a very good way.
We hope to be able to find him and meet  him on one of our many trips to Louisiana.

VERY FUNNY SHOW. SHELBY STANGA FROM "AX-MEN" IS THE BEST CHARACTER OF THE SHOW. FUNNY AND ENERGETIC. MY WIFE LOVES HIM AND HIS SHORT SHORTS, VERY FUNNY ENTERTAINING STUFF. { MAKE MORE} WE NEED MORE OF THE LEGEND OF SHELBY THE SWAMP MAN. THANKS
I love Shelby and I love this DVD with all of his episodes on Ax Men plus the extras.  I hope the producers decide to give us more of his life besides on Ax Men like this DVD.

I really enjoy a lot of reality tv shows like Ice Road Truckers, Swamp People, Ghost Hunters, etc., but this one seems extremely staged to me and very corny.  Shelby tries too hard and comes off as a stupid, loud drama queen that you can't hardly understand.  I've watched the first four episodes and will probably watch the rest because I work hard for my money, but I won't buy the next season.
I love Shelby and wish you had more dvds.
language is horrible. Had to throw it in the recycle bin.
so/so,, he's running around like a chikn with its head cut off most of the time,, his voice aggravate's me,,, but,,,,,,,,,,
Arrived on time. Makes me laugh!!! Funniest show ever made! Thanks Shelby
